OL,3,CGas firm to face criminal charge over
OL,4,Cexplosion in family home
OL,6,FThe company Island Energy will be
OL,7,Fcriminally charged over a gas
OL,8,Fexplosion at a family home in Jersey.
OL,10,FThey have been accused of failing to
OL,11,Fensure the health and safety of
OL,12,Fpersons not in their employment,
OL,13,Fincluding the public, following an
OL,14,Finvestigation by the independent
OL,15,Fworkplace health and safety regulator.
OL,17,FA family of four, including children
OL,18,Faged two and five, were taken to
OL,19,Fhospital after their house at Mont
OL,20,FPinel in St Saviour exploded in June
OL,21,Flast year.
