OL,3,CGas firm to face criminal charge over
OL,4,Cexplosion in family home
OL,6,FJersey Gas, which trades under the
OL,7,Fname Island Energy, has been summoned
OL,8,Fto the island's Magistrate's Court
OL,9,Ffollowing the Health and Safety
OL,10,FInspectorate's investigation, with the
OL,11,Fcase expected to be heard on Thursday
OL,12,F4 December.
OL,14,FThis incident is separate from the
OL,15,FHaut du Mont gas explosion in December
OL,16,F2022, which destroyed a block of flats
OL,17,Fand killed 10 people - with Island
OL,18,FEnergy facing similar criminal charges
OL,19,Funder Health and Safety Law.
